{"tid":370841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢啲係咪叫有緣無份？","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T10:33:33.000Z","uid":113818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dae702661105707c12e597d1c1f99e2170eab43f","tid":370841,"uid":113818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"話說識咗個女仔b小姐都2年，大家都會傾下密計咁，關係都幾close，其實大家都應該知互相對方有feel，不過就係未去到男女朋友階段。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚就同b小姐傾計啦，傾落就知道原來前排一直有個男仔c君追緊b，而b都有應約，不過b始終都係冇接受c，問落之下就知原來b一直都放唔低另一個男仔，不過唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後唔知係邊到嚟嘅勇氣，我走去問佢有冇鍾意過我，我地先終於第一次對對方坦白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，成個夜晚我地都可惜大家冇做主動去追過對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今朝訓醒後唔知點解個心情好down<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲有過呢啲經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ad392cb9813ebf1abe5ead948f19e6f2325285","tid":370841,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28e7a19bd643ad13583e0ce2efbd11bb167b27f","tid":370841,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢有冇鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪係 講完又唔講埋落去"},{"pid":"afe7ee239f5c0f42b59103f4be53be8b49f47261","tid":370841,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"大家仲有鍾意對方咪一齊囉"},{"pid":"15f5124139ec10ad48868300fca4c60f653e5096","tid":370841,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"加油 再追下"},{"pid":"